data.description: Nestled on 1.1 acres near Duck Creek Lake and Lake Michigan, this 4-bed, 3-bath haven boasts a 2-stall garage, storage shed, and play set. The backyard, enveloped by trees for privacy and leading to a scenic walking path to Duck Creek, provides a secluded retreat. The main floor's master suite with a private bath adds an extra touch of indulgence. HOA's snow removal for the main road ensures hassle-free winters. Don't miss this rare opportunity to own a dream home seamlessly combining comfort and captivating surroundings. Schedule your showing now and elevate your lifestyle!
